sub_title: CEO This Is New Africa Services Holding BV. Agricultural equipment, Agricultural projects, Transport LCL and FCL, Automotive, Gambia, Ghana and Democratic Republic of Congo
summary:
We work in a diverse and challenging environment. Together with local governments and farmers associations we are looking for ways to increase rural outcomes and increase the quality of many lives on a responsible way. To preserve forests and wildlife we are developing carbon credits projects with local governments and farmers in the Democratic Republic of Congo. Benefits of the carbon credits projects will be invested in infrastructure, education, food security and health care. 
This Is New Africa Services Holding BV is active in several branches. Our logistical company TINASservices BV is specialized in sending LCL and FCL shipments to the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC) and Ghana. Our trading company TINAStrading DRC Sarl based in Kinshasa is specialized in distributing agricultural equipment and seeds to the DRC. TINASautomotive is specialized in exporting automotive parts, tools and vehicles to African countries. Myself, I am specialized in high risk project management & business development.
